<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1949-11-23T19:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1949-11-23T19:00:00-05:00" n="1408" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1408">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">393.1115/11–1649: Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of
                                    State</gloss> to the Consul General at Taipei</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Macdonald</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-11-23T19:00:00-05:00">November
                                    23, 1949—7 p. m.</date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>483. Deptel 462 Nov 15<note n="86" xml:id="d1408fn86">Not printed.</note>
                            and urtel 707 Nov 16 view deep concern with which highest qtrs Wash
                            regard this matter, report immed all developments to date. Dept awaiting
                            receipt Terry’s mailed report re Taiwan evac details (Manila’s 2628 Nov
                                19<note n="86" xml:id="d1408fn85">Not printed.</note>).</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Webb</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>